{"type": "article", "id": 5117, "title": "Icecap 冰酒器", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-12T07:55:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233803BOYs8RbnTyWL95cV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-color:#000000;-webkit-text-stroke-width:initial;\">\r\n\t来自英国的工程师 Peter Provart 因为喜欢喝酒的缘故，设计了一款可以帮助饮品快速降温的工具 Icecap。这款冰酒器使用前需要放于冰箱冷冻，使用时将冰酒器放于杯子上，酒类饮料等经过内部的管道流入杯中，便可以将其冷却降温至不高于 10C°。突然想要喝冰镇饮品的话，Icecap 可就能帮上忙了。定价 34.99 美元（约合人民币 217 元），<a href=\"https://www.quirky.com/shop/418-icecap-wine-chiller-aerator#inventor\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试预购</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODY5NDQzNDI4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n</iframe>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052338025AutYj2nKgE0GV3e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233802b35P1wp0SIYLl2j8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233802ez6gAR274b90aVLI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}